  <products>
    <product image="maps-48x48.png" href="http://www.microsoft.com/maps/choose-your-bing-maps-API.aspx" target="w_BingDevCenter">
      <header>Maps</header>
      <subtext>Building with Bing Maps</subtext>
      <content>
        <![CDATA[
          <p>Bing Maps Platform offers a set of APIs to incorporate the latest maps, 
          imagery and location services in your application.</p>
        ]]>
      </content>
      <link target="w_BingDevCenter" href="http://www.microsoft.com/maps/choose-your-bing-maps-API.aspx">Find out more</link>
    </product>
    <product image="speech-48x48.png?dt=20130918" href="speech">
      <header>Speech</header>
      <subtext>Interacting with voice</subtext>
      <content>
        <![CDATA[
          <p>Get Bing Speech capabilities integrated with your Windows Phone and Windows Store apps.</p>
        ]]>
      </content>
      <link href="speech">Find out more</link>
    </product>
    <product image="ocr-48x48.png" href="ocr">
      <header>OCR Control</header>
      <subtext>Capture characters</subtext>
      <content>
        <![CDATA[
          <p>The Bing Optical Character Recognition (OCR) Control detects printed text from images 
          captured by the device camera. </p>
      ]]>
      </content>
      <link href="ocr">Find out more</link>
    </product>
    <product image="translator-48x48.png" href="translator">
      <header>Translator</header>
      <subtext>Your window to the world</subtext>
      <content>
        <![CDATA[
          <p>The Bing Translator Control and Microsoft Translator API receive text and deliver 
          automatic machine translation into a specified language.</p>
        ]]>
      </content>
      <link href="translator">Find out more</link>
    </product>
    <product image="ads-48x48.png" href="http://adsinapps.microsoft.com/" target="w_BingDevCenter">
      <header>Ads SDK</header>
      <subtext>Monetize your ideas</subtext>
      <content>
        <![CDATA[
          <p>Whether you're developing in HTML or XAML, the Microsoft Advertising SDK has made it
          easy to insert ads into your Windows 8 and Windows 8.1 apps.</p>
        ]]>
      </content>
      <link target="w_BingDevCenter" href="http://adsinapps.microsoft.com/">Find out more</link>
    </product>
    <product image="bing-ads-api-48x48.png" href="http://developers.bingads.com/" target="w_BingDevCenter">
      <header>Ads API</header>
      <subtext>Manage ads on Bing &amp; Yahoo</subtext>
      <content>
        <![CDATA[
          <p>The Bing Ads API enables advertisers, agencies, and 3rd parties manage their Ads accounts more effectively.</p>
        ]]>
      </content>
      <link target="w_BingDevCenter" href="http://developers.bingads.com/">Find out more</link>
