      <header>Search API</header>
      <subtext>Search by Microsoft​</subtext>
      <content>
        <![CDATA[
          <p>The Bing Search API enables developers to embed search results in applications.</p>
      ]]>
      </content>
      <link target="w_BingDevCenter" href="https://ssl.bing.com/webmaster/developers/appids">Sign in for high volume customers</link>
      <link target="w_BingDevCenter" href="http://download.microsoft.com/download/0/4/E/04E076D4-60B2-4D31-BCC7-C4805B558DBB/Bing%20product%20guidelines.pdf">Review brand attribution guidelines</link>
